I attended PyData Delhi 2017 over this weekend which was the first conference organized by PyData Delhi chapter at IIIT Delhi. In fact, it’s one of the first PyData conferences in India. If you wish to be a part of the community, join the meetup group.&nbsp; 
The conference was organised at the beautiful campus of IIIT Delhi.
 I had a lot of fun and learned a lot over the two days of conference.
